name: Ken Martz
what_you_do: Dr. Ken Martz is a psychologist who specializes in helping men conquer anxiety and achieve emotional freedom.
who_you_serve: Men who are looking to overcome anxiety and improve their emotional well-being.
social_proof: Dr. Ken Martz has over 30 years of experience and has been featured in various media outlets such as Business Insider and CBS.
signature_programs: Unshakable Program, books, counseling services, and keynote presentations.
business_focus: Helping men discover emotional freedom through counseling, speaking, and educational resources.
